ne-ipad-december-14th/|title='Life is Strange' comes to iPhone and iPad December 14th|first=Rob|last=LeFebvre|date=12 December 2017|website=[[Engadget]]}}</ref><ref name=\"Riaz-Jun2018\">{{cite web|url=https://www.hardcoregamer.com/2018/06/04/life-is-strange-arrives-next-month-for-android-exclusive-controller-support-confirmed/301109/|title=Life Is Strange Arrives Next Month for Android, Exclusive Controller Support Confirmed|first=Adnan|last=Riaz|date=4 June 2018|website=Hardcore Gamer|archivedate=4 June 2018|archiveurl=https://archive.today/20180604155316/https://www.hardcoregamer.com/2018/06/04/life-is-strange-arrives-next-month-for-android-exclusive-controller-support-confirmed/301109/|url-status=live|access-date=4 June 2018|df=dmy-all}}</ref>\n\n==Reception==\n{{VG Series Reviews\n| gr    = no\n| game1 = Complete Season\n| mc1   = (PC) 83/100<ref name=\"MCPCCOMP\">{{cite web |url=https://www.metacritic.com/game/pc/life-is-strange |title=Life is Strange for PC Reviews |work=[[Metacritic]] |publisher=[[CBS Interactive]] |accessdate=10 August 2018}}</ref><br />(PS4) 85/100<ref name=\"MCPS4COMP\">{{cite web |url=https://www.metacritic.com/game/playstation-4/life-is-strange |title=Life is Strange for PlayStation 4 Reviews |work=[[Metacritic]] |publisher=[[CBS Interactive]] |accessdate=10 August 2018}}</ref><br />(XONE) 85/100<ref name=\"MCXONECOMP\">{{cite web |url=https://www.metacritic.com/game/xbox-one/life-is-strange |title=Life is Strange for Xbox One Reviews |work=[[Metacritic]] |publisher=[[CBS Interactive]] |accessdate=10 August 2018}}</ref><br />(iOS) 83/100<ref name=\"MCiOSCOMP\">{{cite web |url=https://www.metacritic.com/game/ios/life-is-strange |title=Life is Strange for iPhone/iPad Reviews |work=[[Metacritic]] |publisher=[[CBS Interactive]] |accessdate=8 September 2018}}</ref>\n| game2 = Episode 1: Chrysalis\n| mc2   = (PC) 77/100<ref name=\"MCPCEP1\">{{cite web |url=https://www.metacritic.com/game/pc/life-is-strange-episode-1---chrysalis |title=Life is